{
  "stem": "21978.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she has been on-- in six months aborted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They operated on her to abort her to know if a woman can survive six months abortion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She did survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she was sent to gas chamber afterwards, anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was time when Annetta and I, we had to carry corpses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every time, every day, there were people dying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the corpses were lying behind the barracks heaped up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were most of them, most of the time naked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because the clothing that the dead people had was taken away by other prisoners in the survivor urge.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, the dead ones didn't need it anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So if somebody had still something on that you could use, you could be warmer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could exchange for your dirty or torn garment, it was taken off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Annetta and I, we had to-- I remember close-- very, very clearly one occasion-- there were many more, but one occasion.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was dark, and we hit to be there with the corpses, which were a big pile.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had to take one the hands, one the arms, one the legs and heap them up on the lorry.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "On the lorry, somebody else was standing, piling them up higher, higher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The sight of those corpses was dreadful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because not only they were skeletons and sickly looking, we couldn't see if somebody was there whom we knew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because you didn't recognize even your own friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Some of them have even pus, you know, oozing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Bandages-- if there were bandages, were only paper bandages, crepe bandage, was hanging down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I remember one corpse had half of the face eaten up by rat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Work like that had to be done.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we couldn't shrink from it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had to do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
